  "detailed_description": "Help King Meow to travel the world to find it's missing gold coin!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/bc509272cc56b04d053ee43bd694d608.poster.avif?t=1680065967\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/bc509272cc56b04d053ee43bd694d608.webm?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/bc509272cc56b04d053ee43bd694d608.mp4?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Super Greedy Cat is a platformer where you explore different level with multiple enemies.<br>Do specific challenge to collect Stars at the end of the levels.<br>Each coin gives you a speed boost during 2 seconds which can be cumulated 10 times.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/db27c440f1a3b4dd1cbf32f3ce6f87c5.poster.avif?t=1680065967\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/db27c440f1a3b4dd1cbf32f3ce6f87c5.webm?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/db27c440f1a3b4dd1cbf32f3ce6f87c5.mp4?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Key Features of version 1.0.0:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 20 level campaign<br></li><li> Steam leaderbard<br></li><li> Steam achievements<br></li><li> 60 Challenges</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Roadmap:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Level editor</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Help King Meow to travel the world to find it's missing gold coin!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/bc509272cc56b04d053ee43bd694d608.poster.avif?t=1680065967\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/bc509272cc56b04d053ee43bd694d608.webm?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/bc509272cc56b04d053ee43bd694d608.mp4?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Super Greedy Cat is a platformer where you explore different level with multiple enemies.<br>Do specific challenge to collect Stars at the end of the levels.<br>Each coin gives you a speed boost during 2 seconds which can be cumulated 10 times.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/db27c440f1a3b4dd1cbf32f3ce6f87c5.poster.avif?t=1680065967\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/db27c440f1a3b4dd1cbf32f3ce6f87c5.webm?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127920/extras/db27c440f1a3b4dd1cbf32f3ce6f87c5.mp4?t=1680065967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Key Features of version 1.0.0:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 20 level campaign<br></li><li> Steam leaderbard<br></li><li> Steam achievements<br></li><li> 60 Challenges</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Roadmap:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Level editor</li></ul>",
